\newlabel{fig:stage-ablation-trajectory}{{3}{10}{Two-panel trade-off trajectory showing ROUGE-2 versus absolute summary length distance for the Base and Instruct backbones on VietNews (left) and WikiLingua (right). Arrowed lines display the observed stage sequence (Raw $\rightarrow $ SFT $\rightarrow $ SFT+GRPO v5), while standalone markers show the lower content scores of Fresh GRPO v5 without SFT initialization.\relax }{figure.caption.11}{}}
